Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:33.37,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,657)}{\fad(500,0)}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:37.46,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to act tough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:44.25,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scribbling someone made...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:50.05,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,On the wall, of a flower is swaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:55.64,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows their true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.93,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we both lose and gain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.35,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,By embarking on this long, long path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:09.03,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}And though there may be days loneliness strikes and makes us weep...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:16.54,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's transform our tears and pains to stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.54,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's light a candle to illuminate our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:27.67,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll hold our small hands over the fire to create stardust,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:32.89,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And an eternity that shines so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.27,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewells may be unavoidable,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:44.19,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Yet the seasons continue to change obliviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.28,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose myself, I'll continue to walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:52.32,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.58,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}That's the only thing I'd like to never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:37.46,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,強がらなくていいんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:44.25,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが描いてった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:50.05,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,壁の落書きの花が　揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:55.64,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,自分らしさなんて, 誰もわからないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.93,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,長い長い道の途中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.35,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,失くしたり, 拾ったり,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:09.03,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}急に寂しくなって, 泣いちゃう日もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:16.54,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}涙も　痛みも　星に変えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.54,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}明日を照らす　灯りをともそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:27.67,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さな手かざして　ふたりで作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:32.89,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,星屑を　強く光る永遠を探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.27,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,さよなら　いつかは来るかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:44.19,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}季節はそれでも巡り巡ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.28,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さく迷っても　歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:52.32,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,君と歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.58,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}それだけは変わらないでいようね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:37.46,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaranakute iindane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:44.25,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka ga kaitetta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:50.05,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabe no rakugaki no hana ga yureru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:55.64,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibunrashisa nante dermo wakaranaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.93,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai nagai michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.35,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakushitari hirottari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:09.03,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kyuu ni samishikunatte naichau hi mo arukedo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:16.54,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Namida mo itami mo hoshi ni kaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.54,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ashita wo terasu akari wo tomosou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:27.67,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisana te kazashite futari de tsukurou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:32.89,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshikuzu wo tsuyoku hikaru eien wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.27,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayonara itsuka wa kurukamoshirenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:44.19,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kisetsu wa soredemo meguri megutteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.28,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisaku mayottemo aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:52.32,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi to aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.58,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}Sore dake wa kawaranaideiyoune
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.57,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you still haven't had a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're an important human sacrifice candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:47.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We need you to stay healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.00,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Doctor Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:53.55,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking for some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.01,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...as to what you mean by "human sacrifice"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:02.51,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...and about what you are trying to make me do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.65,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,What you are trying to do right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:12.77,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...is to create a giant transmutation circle, using this country and its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.32,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,And the purpose of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.28,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...is to create a philosopher's stone. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.78,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're close. On the right track, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.16,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,On the right track?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.34,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:29.67,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to help us out, we'll destroy that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.04,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:39.05,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lend us a hand as long as we promise to leave that village alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.75,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.31,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help us out and kill everyone in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:50.56,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you refuse and let everyone in that village die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:55.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing something minor,\Nyou'd be able to save something major.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple concept if you just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:05.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's what makes you guys human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.95,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Emotion always gets in the way of logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same way with that guy I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:15.59,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,When I transformed into his wife, he couldn't fight back and lost his chance to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:20.63,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's really helpful to us that you humans are so vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:36.40,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to me you're really struggling against these humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:37.77,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:45.36,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,To let Scar get away and even have Gluttony captured is unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.54,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.12,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.54,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I won't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.54,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:03.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived for sixty years, and now, I stand at the top of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.94,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,All according to Father's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.98,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:17.31,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang, the Elric brothers,\Nand the ones who come from a foreign land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:22.57,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We, the wise ones, are being thrown into complete disarray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:30.83,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It may just be it's almost time for the young ones to take over the generation, Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.68,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath, you've interacted with humans for far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.34,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:42.59,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to remember what exactly we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:50.22,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I won't report to Father that earlier statement, which could be interpreted as treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.35,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we need to rescue Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.66,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:59.36,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I have a vague idea of their location based on information I received from the military police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.30,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.63,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't provoke him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's only after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.10,Default,Glu,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.03,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan! We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.94,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,What... happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.94,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,The monster was keeping another monster inside its belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.78,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It swallowed everything around him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So even something like this is created...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...by alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.33,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other choice. I'll have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, we were finally able to capture a Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Staying alive is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.96,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he knows our names and our appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to let him go alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He swallowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You really are useless, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't {\i1}you{\i0} try to do something about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:35.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,More like, stop following us! He's only after you, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Run into the bushes! Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... talk about bad timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.79,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.40,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! There's no reason to stay here any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.58,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,But Ed and the others are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.62,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.62,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:19.41,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Getting dragged into some ridiculous battle like this and dying doesn't sound too great to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.17,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.17,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking them so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.89,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Roy Mustang!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.48,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like he fell for the dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem too happy about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up and go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, you're on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Lan Fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:02.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to shamelessly run away in this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.55,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You're really not helping at all, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this stupid Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just do your own job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:19.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that the highest ranked man in this country is a Homunculus isn't exactly a problem you can brush aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The highest ranked man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.77,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean, Führer President Bradley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.42,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.77,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hop in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there aren't any more empty seats.\NJust go ahead without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.09,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:37.03,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can just abandon you kids on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.41,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent is the upper echelon of the army, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:45.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We have to beat some information out of that Gluttony guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stay here and fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter that we're kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who came up with this, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for lending us a hand up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to use it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's something used for killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.98,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's something to protect your lives with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:21.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands aren't meant for killing people. {ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.83,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die. {ep23}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be borrowing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.32,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Please, take care of Lan Fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.01,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.43,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.02,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.76,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the types that end up dying early!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.23,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.46,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Roy Mustang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.66,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you kill Lust...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:13.09,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I said we'd fight him, but he's kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.08,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a whole new person now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to capture him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:23.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.31,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-It talked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.99,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.78,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:58.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a flea-sized runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:04.22,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! I just came to pick up Gluttony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.60,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intentions of fighting mister runt--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seventh time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.39,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Twice just now, and fives times back at Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All told, you've called me a runt seven times!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.65,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got such a good memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.82,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Giving me so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.99,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Mustang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.66,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed Lust!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.66,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to swallow him! Swallow him all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.83,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that to the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.96,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Not to the Elric brothers, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.33,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.09,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.59,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,How many people do you have inside of you, Homunculus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the kid who crossed swords with Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.47,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "kid"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:51.35,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the 12th Prince of the Xing Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.31,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.02,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You can swallow him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.56,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you can't do anything to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin, we'll leave him to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills that were enough to challenge Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.01,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.51,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He got the highest grade in his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.55,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,On the essay he wrote about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.72,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... do you mind if I read it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.22,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Not at the dinner table, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.44,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.06,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:36.73,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.57,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,My father is the Führer President of Amestris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:46.24,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He works hard every day for this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:51.83,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He's always thinking about his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:57.79,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He's constantly trying to find solutions to problems so that everyone can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:04.59,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how busy he is,\Nhe has never forgotten that he has a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.97,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:12.77,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,My father always listens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.44,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He always respects my wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.02,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I love my father and everything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.07,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Selim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.91,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.95,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.66,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.70,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.42,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's something you humans can't do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Now... do you want to be strangled to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.84,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Or bitten to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.01,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Or cut to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.76,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:05.99,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're cheap, kicking dirt into my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:10.62,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There have been many assassination attempts on me, ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I've had to learn a few cheap tricks of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.96,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? Can't you just give up and turn yourself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.42,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I just want information about immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.59,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to get hurt, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.17,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.26,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a human! Don't be looking down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:31.18,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate humans, Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.60,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.65,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to eat you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.90,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat that guy with the thin eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.12,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, don't be interfering with--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.79,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're a human, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.17,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Gluttony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:05.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:06.80,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.59,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I can't let him swallow human sacrifices!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.14,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.83,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I swallowed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, spit him out! Spit out my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.84,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I swallowed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine, right, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:10.03,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the rooms my wife and kids used to live in, but if I have too many lights on, the neighbors will get suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.99,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have to sleep in my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.20,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have to go to the young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.37,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.87,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do in that state?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.72,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He still hasn't returned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.85,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be on my way to Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:45.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.73,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.24,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find out who's on our side and who's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.95,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, the whole lot of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:17:00.49,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to push yourself,\Neven though your wound hasn't healed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:04.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President might be a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We just left some kids on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:16.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be setting a bad example as\Nan adult if I don't take action now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.56,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:27.94,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about how mad Edward would be if he knew you were treating him like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I was just repeating your words, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.69,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I would have never expected you to take such a bold step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.07,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't bold at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.24,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to clear the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:42.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:48.29,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Have a lot of people who understand and are willing to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little late, but I'm going to take his advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:10.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This could either be the gates of glory or an entrance to a den of evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:16.07,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me, I want you to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.16,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the stubborn one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.41,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.33,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely come back, so wait for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.50,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.92,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Roy Mustang, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.05,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from my wife earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:44.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Raven! I deeply apologize for not coming to introduce myself to you due to duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm terribly sorry for visiting you at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.52,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.56,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,How's the old geezer Grumman doing these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.07,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.40,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.91,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's eleven losses in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.41,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Make that twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.58,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you put up a good fight this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.91,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,You started to lose your touch right after you started to think you had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying I let up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:14.34,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You're not able to become heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.13,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,General Raven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,From Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.88,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,He's exceptional, but very soft-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:28.39,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,There was a case where he ran in to rescue one of his men, who was injured, and ended up disrupting his formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:31.19,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,If he's like that, he'll need a lot of men on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.56,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,W-What an insult!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:37.69,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I was employed at Central because of the way I treat my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.15,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,A geezer out on the frontier has no right to say that about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.16,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,M-My apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.74,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:52.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, seeing how you got angry at this,\Nyou must be a man of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:56.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Grumman told me I should go to you in times of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:02.01,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,So that sly dog one-upped me again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.85,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's almost time for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.31,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.31,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:20.07,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite. I'm trying to bring myself to talk with the people more, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.57,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,They've got rumors flying around all over the place, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:27.07,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But most of those rumors are nonsensical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:32.58,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Something about Scar feeding a cat, immortal beings, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:37.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...something about the Führer President being a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.84,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a great sense of humor, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.09,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really work under Grumman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I didn't pick that up from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:54.48,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even gossip like that may end up entertaining everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.15,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I really allowed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:12.25,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,So, about that earlier joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.54,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,About the Führer President being a Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.54,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Colonel Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:28.30,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What about me being a Homunculus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.81,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I get it, Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.19,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,When you said that the army was in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...you didn't mean a crisis was approaching the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.91,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You meant that the army itself was in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.20,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've arrived at the depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:06.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:08.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:27.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:04.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Do people search for the lost because they fear being alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:09.13,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But even if he can't see them, he won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:10.84,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because he believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:16.43,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:19.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 25, Doorway of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.18,0:24:22.77,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:25.10,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at this figure.
